import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; import api from '../config/api'; import '../styles/Resources.css'; function Resources() { const [quote, setQuote] = useState(null); const [loading, setLoading] = useState(true); const [error, setError] = useState(''); const fetchQuote = async () => { setLoading(true); setError(''); try { const response = await api.get('/quote'); setQuote(response.data); } catch (err) { console.error('Error fetching quote:', err); setError('Failed to load quote'); // Set fallback quote setQuote({ content: "Peace comes from within. Do not seek it without.", author: "Buddha", source: 'fallback' }); } finally { setLoading(false); } }; useEffect(() => { fetchQuote(); }, []); return (

Box Breathing

Used by Navy SEALs to stay calm under pressure

4-7-8 Breathing

Dr. Andrew Weil's technique for relaxation

  • Inhale for 4 counts
  • Hold for 7 counts
  • Exhale for 8 counts
  • Repeat 4 times
ü´Å

Diaphragmatic Breathing

Deep belly breathing for stress relief

  • Place hand on belly
  • Breathe deeply into belly
  • Feel belly rise and fall
  • Slow, controlled breaths
